           This  function will return the text position of the internal cursor
           and the directionality of the text at that position.  The  position
           returned is the original text position of the character.


       uuccssttrriinngg__sseett__ccuurrssoorr__mmoottiioonn(())
           This  function  will  change  the cursor motion type and return the
           previous cursor motion type.


       uuccssttrriinngg__ccuurrssoorr__rriigghhtt(())
           This function will move the internal cursor to the right  according
           to the type of cursor motion set for the string.

           If  no cursor motion is performed, it returns 0.  Otherwise it will
           return a 1.


